{
  "version": 1,
  "pages": [
    {
      "id": "team-home",
      "nav_label": "Team home",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "id": "welcome",
          "type": "title",
          "eyebrow": "Shared workspace",
          "title": "Team home",
          "body": "Keep the context your team needs to make progress in one calm, dependable place."
        },
        {
          "id": "starter-status",
          "type": "status",
          "tone": "info",
          "label": "Starter page",
          "text": "Ready to personalize from dashboard.team_pages in config.yaml."
        },
        {
          "id": "starter-kpis",
          "type": "kpi",
          "title": "Personalization at a glance",
          "items": [
            { "label": "Page source", "value": "Config-ready" },
            { "label": "Block types", "value": "7" },
            { "label": "Apply changes", "value": "Reload" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "quick-links",
          "type": "links",
          "title": "Quick links",
          "items": [
            {
              "label": "Work board",
              "description": "Plan and review multi-agent work.",
              "href": "/kanban"
            },
            {
              "label": "Sessions",
              "description": "Return to recent conversations and runs.",
              "href": "/sessions"
            },
            {
              "label": "System health",
              "description": "Check services, runtime, and operations.",
              "href": "/system"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "starter-table",
          "type": "table",
          "title": "Make this page yours",
          "columns": ["Section", "What to add", "Owner"],
          "rows": [
            ["Priorities", "This week's outcomes", "Team lead"],
            ["Links", "Runbooks and project resources", "Operations"],
            ["Status", "Current health and decisions", "Project owner"]
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "configuration-help",
          "type": "markdown",
          "content": "### How personalization works\nAdd `dashboard.team_pages.pages` to `~/.fabric/config.yaml`, then reload the dashboard. Each page can mix title, text, markdown, links, KPI, table, and status blocks.\n\n- Keep the page focused on decisions and shared context.\n- Link to the systems that own detailed work.\n- Use status color only when it communicates meaning."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "engineering",
      "nav_label": "Engineering",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "id": "engineering-title",
          "type": "title",
          "eyebrow": "Starter template",
          "title": "Engineering",
          "body": "A lightweight front door for delivery health, active work, and the links engineers use every day."
        },
        {
          "id": "engineering-status",
          "type": "status",
          "tone": "neutral",
          "label": "Template",
          "text": "Replace these examples with the signals and resources your team already trusts."
        },
        {
          "id": "engineering-guidance",
          "type": "text",
          "title": "What belongs here",
          "body": "Use a small number of high-signal items: delivery health, active incidents, the current goal, and links to source-of-truth systems."
        },
        {
          "id": "engineering-links",
          "type": "links",
          "title": "Engineering tools",
          "items": [
            {
              "label": "Kanban",
              "description": "See planned and in-flight work.",
              "href": "/kanban"
            },
            {
              "label": "Logs",
              "description": "Investigate runtime activity.",
              "href": "/logs"
            },
            {
              "label": "Analytics",
              "description": "Review usage and delivery signals.",
              "href": "/analytics"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "engineering-checklist",
          "type": "table",
          "title": "Suggested operating view",
          "columns": ["Signal", "Question", "Cadence"],
          "rows": [
            ["Delivery", "What is moving or blocked?", "Daily"],
            ["Reliability", "Does anyone need to act?", "Live"],
            ["Decisions", "What changed and why?", "Weekly"]
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
